title: MAY 27 2022 - TERROR IN TEXAS, THE FULL TIMELINE OF UVALDE
description:
Posobiec lays out the full timeline of the Uvalde Elementary School shooting and calls for Texas Governor Abbott to launch an investigation. Posobiec provides an in-depth analysis of China’s leaked audio containing invasion plans for Taiwan. How might America respond should it be more than a ruse? Former U.S. Secretary of State, Henry Kissenger urges Ukraine to seek peace with Russia, even at the expense of ceding territory. Ukraine has repeatedly ruled out ceding territory to Russia, citing: “I think Mr. Kissinger still lives in the 20th century.” Finally, Hollywood Star, and former “King of Davos”, Kevin Spacey is charged with the sexual assault of three men in the U.K.. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
